      <title>嘉能可将于下周宣布是否剥离煤炭业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/glencore-to-announce-future-of-coal-mining-business-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[嘉能可公司 (Glencore Plc) 将于下周在业绩发布会上宣布是否计划剥离煤炭业务。该公司本月初完成了对泰克资源有限公司 (Teck Resources Ltd.) 矿山的收购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/glencore-to-announce-future-of-coal-mining-business-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 06:20:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
